<h3>Smart habit formation system</h3>
<p>
    Next, let‚Äôs talk about habit formation without the sickly sweet gamification nonsense. Picture a system that knows where you are and what you should be doing‚Äîand gives you a gentle nudge. Think of it as a less annoying, location-specific life coach that doesn‚Äôt care about your feelings. It encourages you to stick to your goals, whether it‚Äôs actually eating breakfast or not spending another hour mindlessly scrolling. But never goes back to zero, so you don't have that earthshattering feeling of losing all that time. 
